data.description: Great starter home or for those looking to downsize, this home has mountain views and has been recently upgraded. Imagine the holidays gathering in your kitchen with all new stainless steel appliances, new hardware and gorgeous granite countertops! All 3 bedrooms and living room have ceiling fans to supplement the Central Air in the summer and there are so many updates including newly refinished hardwood floors throughout, newer roof 2021, electric tankless on-demand water heater, new vinyl blinds in all rooms, new insulation, new fresh paint inside and out and vapor barrier in the crawl space - all done this year! The bathroom features beautiful custom tile shower surround and there is plenty of storage to be found in the 1 car garage with rafters and shelves. Situated in a quiet neighborhood with schools, shopping and Fort Carson within minutes, this home is just waiting for a new owner to make it their own!
